com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval

Class DeltaHoldoverArrayTrainable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval.GpuTrainable
      • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval.DeltaHoldoverArrayTrainable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataTrainable, Trainable, TrainableDataMask

    public class DeltaHoldoverArrayTrainable
extends GpuTrainable
    Experimental. The idea behind this class is to track for each row the change in value for an objective function over the course of a single training epoch. Rows which are observed to have a high delta are inferred to be "interesting" rows, subject to retention when re-sampling training data between epochs.
